metadata.name: Tsunami
metadata.description: The sea, with its endless expanse and mysterious depths, has always held a certain allure for humans. But when its power is unleashed in the form of a tsunami, the sheer force of the water is awe-inspiring. As the massive wave crashes onto shore, swallowing up everything in its path, it is a reminder of the sublime power of nature. Despite the destruction it can cause, there is something breathtaking about the tsunami, a raw and primal energy that humbles us in its presence.
